title: Jeb Bush targets Hillary Clinton’s Benghazi emails during interview with Pat Robertson
text: Republican presidential candidate Jeb Bush took aim at Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Clinton on Friday after e-mails about the attacks in Benghazi were disclosed during a hearing on Thursday. “It's always this, isn’t it, with the Clintons?” Bush said in an interview with televangelist and one-time GOP presidential candidate Pat Robertson at Regent University.
